  "style": "IEEE",
  "texts": [
    "To promote the adaptability, researchers have improved the architecture of SAM to better deal with specialized challenges, such as camouflaged object detect [30] and medical image analysis [31,32].",
    "For instance, Chen et al. [30] enhance SAM's prompt adaptation capability by introducing a response filter and semantic matcher, thereby improving mask quality in camouflaged object detection scenarios.",
    "HQ-SAM [33] enhances SAM's segmentation precision by integrating a learnable High-Quality Output Token within the mask decoder, leveraging effective fusion of features from ViT layers.",
    "PA-SAM [34] refines SAM's segmentation capabilities through a prompt adapter, which optimizes feature extraction and decoding for improved flexibility and performance.",
    "Hi-SAM [10] realizes hierarchical text segmentation in a unified framework.…… Image EncoderToken to Image Attn."
  ],
